PrecisRe-appointment of MERVYN C. RUSSELL of Halifax, Nova Scotia, as chairman of the board of directors of the Halifax Port Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term effective February 1, 1999 and ending April 30, 1999; and approval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Transport of MERVYN C. RUSSELL, of Halifax, Nova Scotia, as a part-time director of the board of directors of the Canada Ports Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term effective February 1, 1999 and ending April 30, 1999.
